room_title: Escape room "Wonderland" by Paranoia Quest in Atlanta
room_address: 3333 Buford Drive NE, Suite VB03, Buford GA 30519
room_description:
Things have gone terribly wrong in wonderland! The magic clock and time itself has stopped working. Now wonderland is frozen without a morning, noon or night. The only hope left is you.
You need to sneak into the clock tower and fix the magic clock before Wonderland is stuck forever.
